<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/style_sidebar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-header">
            <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="toggleSidebar()">
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
            <h3 class="menu-text">Menu</h3>
        </div>

        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li>
                <a href="#">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
                    <span class="menu-text">Criar Contato</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#">
                    <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>
                    <span class="menu-text">Criar Tarefa</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li class="logout-item">
                <a href="../">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
                    <span class="menu-text">Sair</span>
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main class="content">
        <h1>Bem-vindo <span><%= user.username %></span></h1>
        <p>Fique a vontade para criar tarefas e adcionar contatos em sua agenda.</p>
    </main>

    <script>
        function toggleSidebar() {
            const sidebar = document.getElementById('sidebar');
            sidebar.classList.toggle('collapsed');
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>